data.description: Stunning mobile home nestled on 2.5 acres of wooded land in Montura Ranch Estates. This exceptional residence offers an expansive floor plan including a dining area and an open kitchen designed for entertaining. Home is in immaculate condition and was newly built in 2019. Boasting 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and fireplace for cold winter days. Home has a stunning front deck, beautiful landscape, and gravel walkways. situated on a corner double lot. Ample space to add a guest home or underground pool. No need to remove underbrush.
